access-control-allow-headers: Origin, Content-Type, Authorization, X-Requested-With, User-Agent, Access-Token, User-Id, Time, Sign, X-BC, App-Token, X-Of-Rev, X-Hash, Csrf
access-control-allow-methods: GET, PUT, POST, DELETE, OPTIONS, PATCH
access-control-expose-headers: Content-Length, Content-Range, Date, Access-Token, User-Id, X-OF-REV
